This module shows number of pages in a PDF File
in the statusbar.


............Compile.............

If your machine have x86 processor, edit Makefile and
change LIBDIR from arm-linux-gnueabihf to x86_64-linux-gnu

Install Dependencies...
	libfm-dev
	libpoppler-glib-dev

Run command...
	make


...........Install..............

Run command..
	sudo make install


......Runtime dependencies......
	libpoppler-glib8
